body:
Now, when trying to print the checkpoint graph with `checkpointable_utils._serialize_object_graph(ckpt, None)` it will throw:
```
/python3.5/site-packages/tensorflow/python/keras/_impl/keras/engine/base_layer.py", line 196, in name
    return self._name
AttributeError: 'DropoutWrapper' object has no attribute '_name'
```
